| TYPE | 51 |
| TDATA1 | -(TDATA5+TDATA2) |
| TDATA2 | 0 |
| TDATA3 | -TDATA4 |
| TDATA4 | 0 |
| TDATA5 | 1 |
| TDATA6 | 0 |
